short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: TeraBox Viral Video Link Saver ▷ Save TeraBox Video Links Online to Play + Download Later.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Effortlessly save TeraBox links for future use!
This extension adds a convenient "Save TeraBox URL for Later :)" button to supported TeraBox websites. With just one click, you can save the current page's URL to a dedicated list and access it anytime from the extension popup. Duplicate links are automatically filtered, ensuring your list stays clean and organized.

Features:
One-Click Save: Quickly save TeraBox links directly from the webpage.
Avoid Duplicates: Links are saved only once, no matter how many times you click.
Modern UI: A sleek and user-friendly popup for managing your saved links.
Wide Compatibility: Supports multiple TeraBox-related domains.


How to Use:
Visit any supported TeraBox page.
Click the "Save TeraBox URL for Later :)" button added to the page.
Open the extension popup to view and manage your saved links.
Simplify managing your favorite TeraBox links today!
